{"tid":117011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打想搞個組織推動大麻合法化?","createTime":"2017-02-11T21:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T17:13:39.000Z","uid":40542,"like":19,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1dfb670f36c359836506d0e07eeef7227337ab27","tid":117011,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T21:30:07.000Z","msg":"首先小弟不材，無膽識搞個組織出來，同埋長時間唔係香港，希望有志之士會搞得成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n綜觀宜家香港其實好似未有一個有規模推動大麻合法化嘅組織，雖然越來越多facebook page講大麻係好事，但係其實都係不足。<br />\n小弟希望咁多位連登巴打可以搞個組織出來，一齊推動大麻合法化。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會同本地醫生組織/醫療機構、同唔同政黨、智庫、政府傾吓，整多啲文宣教育普羅大眾，擺下街站宣傳下，<br />\n令到主流社會/立法會討論 --&gt; 藥用大麻合法化 --&gt; 大麻除罪化 --&gt; 娛樂用大麻合法化<br />\n<br />\n我知係好天馬行空，但我信有一日係一定會成功架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0d427291f1ce1a64177a30271196aa13c2bc8d","tid":117011,"uid":5980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T21:46:57.000Z","msg":"有理想係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9240eaf0c6e60213abdf1e986d25ca314f135ece","tid":117011,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T21:50:07.000Z","msg":"好呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131d26d9efb3123b5fcf7e0a5d57881f7b797933","tid":117011,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T22:00:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea440802d0eac9d55a17d02c206d429b02bc8b3f","tid":117011,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T22:14:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ok，畀100k我，我一定搞</blockquote><br />\n見你開個價就知未出嚟做嘢"},{"